com.siperian.sif.message

Class RecordTypes

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.siperian.sif.message.RecordTypes
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class RecordTypes
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Options specifying which record types an associated get operation retrieves.

    By default, a record types object has package type = True and all others (xref type, xref history type, history type, and raw type) = False
